never to go up there.

106
00:13:50,759 --> 00:13:52,909
Lonnie Elam said
that's a haunted house.

107
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:55,196
He said awful stuff
happened there once.

108
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,509
